2011-11-29  Stefan Theussl  <stefan.theussl@wu.ac.at>

	* R/streaming.R (hive_stream): accepts now a streaming_args argument.
	* man/hive_stream.Rd (hive_stream): describes the new
	streaming_args argument.
	* R/handler.R (hive_default_nreducer): calculation of optimal
	reducer size changed to round(n_slaves/1.5).

